Package soot.util.annotations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationElemSwitch
    An AbstractAnnotationElemTypeSwitch that converts an AnnotationElem to a mapping of element name and the actual result.
    AnnotationElemSwitch.AnnotationElemResult<V>
    A helper class to map method name and result.
    AnnotationInstanceCreator
    A simple helper class with the ability to create an instance of Proxy implementing the annotation interface represented by the given AnnotationTag.
    ClassLoaderUtils
    Loads classes without relying on JBoss.
